    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015110/extras/973ac77a71905da4364ec82e8d9fd058.poster.avif?t=1722267639\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015110/extras/973ac77a71905da4364ec82e8d9fd058.webm?t=1722267639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015110/extras/973ac77a71905da4364ec82e8d9fd058.mp4?t=1722267639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Backrooms Cats and Lava</strong> 是一款带有解谜元素的动作平台游戏，您必须帮助一名小居民逃离被岩浆吞没的深洞穴。通过移动箱子导航到出口，但请记住——地面是岩浆！无论如何都要避免踩到它。使用您所有的技能在这个炽热的迷宫中生存下来，并找到逃离这个地狱般的地方的道路。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015110/extras/5b025857fb86a884884438f4b000523c.poster.avif?t=1722267639\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015110/extras/5b025857fb86a884884438f4b000523c.webm?t=1722267639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015110/extras/5b025857fb86a884884438f4b000523c.mp4?t=1722267639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点：</h2></strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的解谜机制：</h2>通过战略性地移动箱子来解决具有挑战性的难题，以创建安全路径并逃离不断上升的岩浆。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >激烈的平台动作：</h2>结合快速反应和聪明的计划，穿越充满危险障碍的越来越难的关卡。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >引人入胜的生存挑战：</h2>测试您的生存技能，避免致命的岩浆地板，并找到创造性的解决方案以逃离每个危险的关卡。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >大气环境：</h2>沉浸在紧张和炽热的洞穴环境中，通过增强的氛围图形和声音效果强化体验。<ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul></li></ul>",
